net.edudb.relational_algebra

Interface RAMatcherChain

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CartesianProductMatcher, EquiJoinMatcher, FilterMatcher, NullMatcher, ProjectMatcher, RelationMatcher

    public interface RAMatcherChain
    An interface, that implements the Chain of Responsibility design pattern, that is used to match relational algebra formulae.
    Author:
    Ahmed Abdul Badie

      • match

        RAMatcherResult match(java.lang.String string)
        Matches the passed relational algebra formula. Classes that implement the RAMatcherChain interface handles the matching of the passed relational algebra formula according to their functionality.
        Parameters:
        string - The relational algebra formula to match.
        Returns:
        The result of matching the passed relational algebra formula.
